messages.content: awesome! Even better than getting it at the same time as other presents. It's really no big deal, but I am curious to see what you send me
so i'm an awful cousin for not mailing out your christmas gift. the holidays were a little crazy for us. i will be sending out your record asap! :) christmas in april!
very cool! we love vinyl, too so i'm sure we can find you something! what is a good address to send you something?

Amazon or Barnes and Noble gift card would be good. Or, I have a record player, so second hand vinyls are always fun to get (any kind of music). Or, you can surprise me if you come across something unique or have something you wanna get rid of.
i have your name for christmas! what would you like? :)
